{"type": "article", "id": 3223, "title": "带触屏功能的手套", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-03T08:17:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232849WGtVISjrKNPiQOLD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t裹着毫不客气的寒风的冬天就要来了，一双温暖的手套一定是必备之选，可“手机控”们在考虑的问题是，如何透过厚厚的手套发微信、刷微博？来自荷兰的设计品牌 MUJJO 日前带来了他们的最新带触屏功能的手套。这双针织手套衬里为羊毛材质，保证了保暖这一基础功能，手腕部分，设计团队还使用了黑色皮质的扣带，凸显质感。而掌心部分的防滑颗粒设计则是专为手机一族的设计，增强使用者拿握时的稳定性。据官方介绍，这款手套可兼容现如今市面上的大多数电容触屏设备，定价 20.62 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.mujjo.com/touchscreen-gloves/refined-touchscreen-gloves\" target=\"_blank\">本月 20 日正式开始发售</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232846Dx9ZoGiUTKQRqrle.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052328477sbif4F6mLgqutw0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232847AzUQp2HylihoV8Xq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232848Ak6PMpoBtQlZFU0S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232848bN9UEzQLhZ2FdHfy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}